        "start": "03:20.500",
        "end": "03:22.000",
        "original": "一生懸命やってんだぞ！",
        "english": "We're doing our best!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:22.500",
        "end": "03:23.500",
        "original": "かわいそう。",
        "english": "Poor thing.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:24.000",
        "end": "03:25.500",
        "original": "いじめないで。",
        "english": "Don't bully him.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:27.500",
        "end": "03:29.000",
        "original": "あずき、あずき。",
        "english": "AZKi, AZKi.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:29.000",
        "end": "03:30.500",
        "original": "あずちゃん優しくしてあげて。",
        "english": "AZ-chan, be nice to him.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:31.500",
        "end": "03:34.000",
        "original": "もっと、床に這いつくばりなさい。",
        "english": "Now, grovel more on the floor.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:34.000",
        "end": "03:37.000",
        "original": "あずき様！？あずき様！？",
        "english": "AZKi-sama!? AZKi-sama!?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:37.500",
        "end": "03:40.500",
        "original": "ありがとね、みんな、来てくれて本当に。",
        "english": "Thank you, everyone, for coming, really.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:40.000",
        "end": "03:41.500",
        "original": "こちらこそ！",
        "english": "Our pleasure!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:41.500",
        "end": "03:43.000",
        "original": "お誕生日おめでとう！",
        "english": "Happy Birthday!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:47.500",
        "end": "03:51.500",
        "original": "じゃあ、なんか、あと、今日は集めてくれてありがとね、本当に。",
        "english": "So, um, also, thanks for gathering everyone today, really.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:54.000",
        "end": "03:57.000",
        "original": "次のテストの時間だから、行ってくるね！",
        "english": "It's time for the next test, so I'm going now!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:57.500",
        "end": "04:00.000",
        "original": "行ってらっしゃい！頑張れ！",
        "english": "Have a safe trip! Good luck!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:00.000",
        "end": "04:01.500",
        "original": "また会いましょう！",
        "english": "Let's meet again!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:01.500",
        "end": "04:04.000",
        "original": "バイバイ！",
        "english": "Bye bye!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:04.500",
        "end": "04:12.000",
        "original": "ゾンビ、もっと祝いなさいよ、祝いなさいよ、もっとゼータを、祝って！",
        "english": "Zombie, celebrate more, celebrate, celebrate Zeta more, celebrate!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:17.500",
        "end": "04:19.500",
        "original": "Wait, there's like a ring.",
        "english": "Wait, there's like a ring.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:19.500",
        "end": "04:22.500",
        "original": "Wait, is this like a boxing ring?",
        "english": "Wait, is this like a boxing ring?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:23.000",
        "end": "04:25.500",
        "original": "Wait, what am I gonna have to do here?",
        "english": "Wait, what am I gonna have to do here?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:26.500",
        "end": "04:30.000",
        "original": "No way. Are we gonna have to fight? I'm not good at fighting though.",
        "english": "No way. Are we gonna have to fight? I'm not good at fighting though.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:30.500",
        "end": "04:32.500",
        "original": "I mean, I can try. Hwah! Hwah! Hwah!",
        "english": "I mean, I can try. Hwah! Hwah! Hwah!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:32.500",
        "end": "04:34.500",
        "original": "Happy birthday, Zeta!",
        "english": "Happy birthday, Zeta!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:34.500",
        "end": "04:35.500",
        "original": "Long time no see!",
        "english": "Long time no see!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:35.500",
        "end": "04:37.000",
        "original": "This is Amelia Watson...",
        "english": "This is Amelia Watson...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:37.500",
        "end": "04:41.500",
        "original": "hololive EN's number one time-traveling detective!",
        "english": "hololive EN's number one time-traveling detective!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:41.500",
        "end": "04:43.000",
        "original": "How've you been?",
        "english": "How've you been?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:43.000",
        "end": "04:45.500",
        "original": "I've been good, how are you!?",
        "english": "I've been good, how are you!?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:46.000",
        "end": "04:48.000",
        "original": "Ah, glad to see you're doing well!",
        "english": "Ah, glad to see you're doing well!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:48.500",
        "end": "04:50.500",
        "original": "Yeah, I prepared the second test...",
        "english": "Yeah, I prepared the second test...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:50.500",
        "end": "04:53.000",
        "original": "but we also have other transfer students.",
        "english": "but we also have other transfer students.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:53.000",
        "end": "04:55.000",
        "original": "Let's call them in now!",
        "english": "Let's call them in now!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:55.500",
        "end": "04:58.000",
        "original": "Don't let the first contestant's size fool you!",
        "english": "Don't let the first contestant's size fool you!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:58.000",
        "end": "05:00.000",
        "original": "People tremble...",
        "english": "People tremble...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
